CRUD Operation project using Spring Boot 4.0.5

Used:
    Java 17
    Spring Boot 4.0.5
    H2 Database

Sample Request:
Post: Add single product:
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/products
Body:
    {
      "name": "Product1",
      "description": "This is a sample product1",
      "price": 19.99
    }


Post: Add multiple products:
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/products/bulk
Body:
    [
      { "name": "Laptop Pro", "description": "High-end workstation for developers", "price": 1200.00 },
      { "name": "Wireless Mouse", "description": "Ergonomic silent click mouse", "price": 25.50 },
      { "name": "Mechanical Keyboard", "description": "RGB backlit with blue switches", "price": 75.99 },
      { "name": "4K Monitor", "description": "27-inch IPS display for designers", "price": 350.00 },
      { "name": "USB-C Hub", "description": "7-in-1 adapter with HDMI and SD ports", "price": 40.00 },
      { "name": "Noise Cancelling Headphones", "description": "Over-ear bluetooth headphones", "price": 199.99 },
      { "name": "Gaming Chair", "description": "Ergonomic leather chair with lumbar support", "price": 250.00 },
      { "name": "Webcam HD", "description": "1080p camera with built-in microphone", "price": 60.45 },
      { "name": "External SSD", "description": "1TB high-speed portable storage", "price": 110.00 },
      { "name": "Smart Watch", "description": "Fitness tracker with heart rate monitor", "price": 150.25 }
    ]


Get All Products:
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/products

Get Product By ID:
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/products/2

Put: Update existing product:
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/products/2
Body:
    {
      "id": 2,
      "name": "Updated Product",
      "description": "Updated description",
      "price": 99.99
    }

Put: Delete existing product:
URL: http://localhost:8080/api/products/3

